        I&#39;m <strong class="text-accent">not only a developer</strong>, I
        truly believe that giving others to be heard makes devs the best
        community in the world and <strong class="text-accent"
          >gives my own voice</strong
        >
        space for <strong class="text-accent">an impact</strong> on those who want
        me to talk to them, that's why <strong class="text-accent"
          >I also do blogs</strong
        > and sometimes when my schedule allows me to do it <strong
          class="text-accent">I give talks</strong
        > and those things I know
      </p>
